title: Bretheon v2.2.6 - Themeforest Premium WordPress Theme

With Bretheon wordpress theme you get totally new & fresh solution for your business. This theme can be used for each kind of page. You can use this product with boxed layout or full width. If you don`t want to configure your own site, you can also import .xml demo file and in few seconds you will get the same page as our demo. It`s so easy and everyone can do that!

Even if you prefer build pages on shortcodes, you can also easily do that. Content Builder contain over 20 items and is really great option for all those who doesn`t want to work with HTML code or even shortcodes.

With this slider you can create any slides you want (single image, images, video, videos, images/objects with text, plain text and anything else what you can imagine).
